}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#936af799b2cff75ccdab93e3144191f1>.
<#936af799b2cff75ccdab93e3144191f1> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/2b84284b-4e01-48ee-8f40-5792c42579f2>;
