    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Automatic weather station data from locations within the distributed Swedish research infrastructure SITES. Check preview or file for the specific parameters included at this location. Data has been quality controlled and cleaned from outliers and other events producing unrealistic data. Gaps have not been filled.\nTarfala Research Station (2025). Meteorological data from Laevasvagge, AWS, 2015-01-01–2015-12-31 [Data set]. Swedish Infrastructure for Ecosystem Science (SITES). https://hdl.handle.net/11676.1/kKpfX6UCcv0m093rB8bKqrDb"@en;
