<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#87f3ce5e56d2e628b45aa7f42d2b8f73>.
<#87f3ce5e56d2e628b45aa7f42d2b8f73> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
