<#608f67c36552fc3d81a61add29182ab5> {
<https://doi.org/10.5878/9qg4-9a30> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Primärvård"@sv, "Cardiovascular Diseases"@en, "Nervsystemets sjukdomar"@sv, "Nervous System Diseases"@en, "Rehabilitering"@sv, "Rehabilitation"@en, "Primary Health Care"@en, "Lungsjukdomar"@sv, "Lung Diseases"@en, "prevention"@sv, "prevention"@en, "Aktiviteter i dagliga livet"@sv, "Activities of Daily Living"@en, "Kronisk smärta"@sv, "Chronic Pain"@en, "Kardiovaskulära sjukdomar"@sv, "Patients"@en, "Patienter"@sv, "Self-Management"@en, "Självstyrning"@sv, "Healthcare organization"@en, "vårdgivare"@sv, "Healthcare professional"@en, "hälso- och sjukvårdspersonal"@sv, "referral processes"@en, "remissvägar"@sv, "experiences"@en, "erfarenheter"@sv, "sjukvårdsorganisation"@en, "healthcare organization"@sv, "care processes"@en, "vårdprocesser"@sv, "professionals"@en, "professioner"@sv, "CHRONIC ILLNESS"@en, "KRONISK SJUKDOM"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__76569.
_:b0__76569 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/59e090bc12e061adf157a7354b975875>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/9qg4-9a30> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__28373.
_:b0__28373 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/c0661155cdaf735296f36a942e1c14ff>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/9qg4-9a30> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/NON_PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021002841>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The data consists of experiences of  proactive self-management efforts among individuals with chronic illnesses and healthcare professionals. Data were collected through five focus group discussions: two with members of patient associations and three with healthcare professionals working at primary care centers. The discussions were conducted in Swedish.\n\nOne of the focus groups with healthcare professionals was held at their primary care unit, while the remaining sessions were conducted digitally. All sessions were audio-recorded. The recordings were transcribed verbatim using Microsoft Word. The transcribed material constitutes the dataset for analysis. A classical focus group analysis was then conducted to identify patterns and themes within the data."@en, "Data består av erfarenheter av insatser för proaktiv self-management hos personer med kronisk sjukdom och hälso- och sjukvårdspersonal. Data inhämtades genom fem fokusgruppsdiskussioner, två med medlemmar i patientföreningar och tre med hälso- och sjukvårdspersonal vid hälsocentraler. Data är på svenska.\n\nEn av fokusgrupperna med hälso- och sjukvårdspersonal genomfördes på deras primärvårdsenhet medan de övriga genomfördes digitalt. Samtliga spelades in via en ljudfil.  Ljudfilerna transkriberades i Microsoft Word. Ljudfilerna transkriberades ordagrant. Transkriberad data utgör datamaterialet. Analys genomfördes sedan med klassisk fokusgruppsanalys för att hitta mönster i data."@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://sws.geonames.org/2661886>, <http://sws.geonames.org/604010>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://doi.org/10.5878/9qg4-9a30#distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2025-09-30T11:27:18.012526Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.5878/9qg4-9a30>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-10-02T07:00:13.686151Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Data from a focus group study involving members of patient organizations and primary care professionals focusing on self-management interventions"@en, "Data från en fokusgruppsstudie med medlemmar i patientorganisationer och vårdpersonal inom primärvården om insatser för self-management"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/HEAL>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__93717.
_:b0__93717 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2025-01-31"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2024-03-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>
