<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#ee8da8e4f6f96116e4c71c7be4f1e53a>.
<#ee8da8e4f6f96116e4c71c7be4f1e53a> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
