<#ee8da8e4f6f96116e4c71c7be4f1e53a> {
<https://opendata.umea.se/api/v2/catalog/datasets/roads_umea> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Umeå kommun", "Vägar"@sv, "Trafikverket"@sv, "Järnvägar"@sv, "Streets"@en, "National Road database"@en, "Järnvägar"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "roads_umea@http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2120002627";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/43/resource/7a00bd3796ed09a600646432cb321722>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Vill du ha information om vägar och järnvägar i kommunen kan du söka denna hos Trafikverket.Trafikverkets öppna data innehåller en mängd information om vägar och järnvägar.Du finner information om deras öppna data här: https://www.trafikverket.se/e-tjanster/hamta-data-fran-trafikverket/ Detta är ett exempel på den data som kan hämtas. Denna datamängd uppdateras (hämtas)  inte regelbundet av denna portal. Vill du ha aktuella data hänvisar vi dig till Trafikverket.."@sv, "If you want information about roads and railways in the municipality, you can find it via the Swedish Transport Administration (Trafikverket).Trafikverket’s open data contains a wide range of information about roads and railways.This dataset contains information about wildlife fences in the municipality.You can find more information about their open data here:[https://www.trafikverket.se/e-tjanster/hamta-data-fran-trafikverket/](https://www.trafikverket.se/e-tjanster/hamta-data-fran-trafikverket/)This is an example of the data that can be retrieved. Please note that this dataset is not regularly updated by this portal. For up-to-date information, we refer you directly to Trafikverket."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://opendata.umea.se/explore/?refine.dcat.contact_name=%C3%96ppna+Data+Ume%C3%A5+kommun&refine.dcat.contact_email=oppnadata%2540umea.se>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-API>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-csv>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-json>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-fgb>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-geojson>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-gpx>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-jsonl>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-kml>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-ov2>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-parquet>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-rdfxml>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-jsonld>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-turtle>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-n3>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-shp>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/roads_umea-xlsx>;
