    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://www.geodata.se/resources/4f5bb0bc-8457-b21b-08ca-428b63b9286b> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <urn:uuid:51f480fd-f27a-e1e8-16d9-7a9817c63d1d>, <urn:uuid:ca5dac5e-b87f-cc21-686d-0ded17af3929>, <urn:uuid:841d9e3c-0250-f6cc-55f6-1b0078901950>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/provenance> _:b0__69679.
_:b0__69679 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#value> "Hämtat och sammanst��llt från Naturvårdsverket"@sv;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
<https://www.geodata.se/resources/4f5bb0bc-8457-b21b-08ca-428b63b9286b> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2025-06-17"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-06-17"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
